<div class="container py-24">
  <div class="text-center mb-16" data-aos="fade-down">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold font-serif text-primary mb-4">Design System Guide</h1>
    <p class="text-gray-600">DLAB의 디자인 시스템 가이드라인입니다.</p>
  </div>

  <!-- 1. Color Palette -->
  <section class="mb-20" data-aos="fade-up">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-8 border-b pb-4">1. Color Palette</h2>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
      <div class="space-y-2">
        <div class="h-24 rounded-lg bg-primary shadow-md"></div>
        <p class="font-bold">Primary</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">#00a859</p>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-2">
        <div class="h-24 rounded-lg bg-[#008a47] shadow-md"></div>
        <p class="font-bold">Primary Dark</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">#008a47</p>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-2">
        <div class="h-24 rounded-lg bg-accent shadow-md"></div>
        <p class="font-bold">Accent</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">#00d670</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-6 mt-8">
      <div class="space-y-2">
        <div class="h-24 rounded-lg bg-emerald-500 shadow-md"></div>
        <p class="font-bold">Success</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Emerald 500</p>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-2">
        <div class="h-24 rounded-lg bg-yellow-500 shadow-md"></div>
        <p class="font-bold">Warning</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Yellow 500</p>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-2">
        <div class="h-24 rounded-lg bg-red-500 shadow-md"></div>
        <p class="font-bold">Error</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Red 500</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 2. Typography -->
  <section class="mb-20" data-aos="fade-up">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-8 border-b pb-4">2. Typography</h2>
    
    <div class="space-y-8 bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
      <div>
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-serif text-primary">Heading 1 (Serif)</h1>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">text-4xl font-serif text-primary</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900">Heading 2 (Sans Bold)</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800">Heading 3 (Sans Semibold)</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
          Body Text (Large): AI 기술과 디자인의 완벽한 조화. 디어스에서 당신의 비즈니스를 혁신하세요.
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">text-lg text-gray-700</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <p class="text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          Body Text (Base): 일반적인 본문 텍스트입니다. 가독성을 위해 적절한 줄간격과 회색톤을 사용합니다.
          Pretendard 폰트가 적용되어 한글이 깔끔하게 표시됩니다.
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">text-base text-gray-600</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 3. Components -->
  <section class="mb-20" data-aos="fade-up">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-8 border-b pb-4">3. Components</h2>

    <!-- Buttons -->
    <div class="mb-12">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">Buttons</h3>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 items-center p-8 bg-gray-50 rounded-xl">
        <button class="btn btn-primary">Primary Button</button>
        <button class="btn btn-outline">Outline Button</button>
        <button class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Large Button</button>
        <button class="btn btn-primary opacity-50 cursor-not-allowed">Disabled</button>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Cards -->
    <div class="mb-12">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">Cards</h3>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div class="card group cursor-pointer">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-emerald-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-primary mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6V4m0 2a2 2 0 100 4m0-4a2 2 0 110 4m-6 8a2 2 0 100-4m0 4a2 2 0 110-4m0 4v2m0-6V4m6 6v10m6-2a2 2 0 100-4m0 4a2 2 0 110-4m0 4v2m0-6V4"></path></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Interactive Card</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            This is a standard card component with interaction states. Hover to see the shadow effect increase.
          </p>
          <span class="text-primary font-bold group-hover:translate-x-2 transition-transform inline-block">Learn more →</span>
        </div>

        <div class="card bg-gray-900 text-white">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-white/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-white mb-6">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Dark Card</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">
            A variation for dark backgrounds or highlighted content.
          </p>
          <span class="text-white font-bold">Action →</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 4. Form Components -->
  <section class="mb-20" data-aos="fade-up">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-8 border-b pb-4">4. Form Elements</h2>
    <div class="max-w-xl mx-auto bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-gray-100">
      <form onsubmit="event.preventDefault(); alert('Form submitted!');" class="space-y-6">
        <div>
          <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-2">Input Field</label>
          <input type="text" placeholder="Enter text..." class="w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-lg border border-gray-300 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary focus:border-transparent outline-none transition-all">
        </div>

        <div>
           <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-2">Select Box</label>
           <select class="w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-lg border border-gray-300 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary focus:border-transparent outline-none transition-all appearance-none bg-white">
             <option>Option 1</option>
             <option>Option 2</option>
           </select>
        </div>

        <div>
          <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-2">Checkbox</label>
          <label class="flex items-center gap-3 cursor-pointer">
            <input type="checkbox" class="w-5 h-5 text-primary rounded border-gray-300 focus:ring-primary">
            <span class="text-gray-700">I agree to the Design System</span>
          </label>
        </div>

        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary w-full">Submit Form</button>
      </form>
    </div>
  </section>
</div>
